subtitleNullable: Evaluating Zero-Shot Time Series Forecasting Capabilities of LLMs
descriptionNullable: The "ZeroShot LLM4TS Benchmark" dataset is designed to evaluate the performance of large language models (LLMs) in zero-shot time series forecasting tasks. The dataset contains various time series data from different domains, providing a comprehensive benchmark for testing LLM capabilities in forecasting without prior training on the specific data.
